dc7482ecedbaea3e549bc140:
WITH LastVisit AS (
    SELECT 
        MAX(hadm_id) AS hadm_id
    FROM 
        admissions
    WHERE 
        subject_id = 10027445
),
WeightMeasurements AS (
    SELECT 
        c.charttime,
        c.valuenum,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY c.charttime) AS rn,
        COUNT(*) OVER () AS total_count
    FROM 
        chartevents c
    INNER JOIN 
        d_items i ON c.itemid = i.itemid
    INNER JOIN 
        LastVisit lv ON c.hadm_id = lv.hadm_id
    WHERE 
        i.label LIKE '%Weight%' AND
        c.subject_id = 10027445
)
SELECT 
    (MAX(CASE WHEN rn = total_count THEN valuenum ELSE NULL END) - 
     MAX(CASE WHEN rn = 1 THEN valuenum ELSE NULL END)) AS weight_change
FROM 
    WeightMeasurements;

WITH HyalineCasts AS (
  SELECT 
    l.charttime,
    l.valuenum AS value,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY l.charttime) AS rn,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY l.charttime DESC) AS rn_desc
  FROM labevents l
  INNER JOIN d_labitems dl ON l.itemid = dl.itemid
  WHERE l.subject_id = 10021487 AND dl.label = 'Hyaline Casts'
)

  (SELECT value FROM HyalineCasts WHERE rn = 1) - 
  (SELECT value FROM HyalineCasts WHERE rn_desc = 1) AS value_difference;

941095e5c2a9df6746e4a383:
SELECT
    (MAX(CASE WHEN ce.charttime = (
        SELECT MAX(charttime)
        FROM chartevents
        WHERE stay_id = icu.stay_id
        AND itemid = di.itemid
    ) THEN ce.valuenum END)) -
    (MAX(CASE WHEN ce.charttime = (
        SELECT MAX(charttime)
        FROM chartevents
        WHERE stay_id = icu.stay_id
        AND itemid = di.itemid
        AND charttime < (
            SELECT MAX(charttime)
            FROM chartevents
            WHERE stay_id = icu.stay_id
            AND itemid = di.itemid
        )
    ) THEN ce.valuenum END)) AS difference
FROM icustays icu
JOIN chartevents ce ON icu.stay_id = ce.stay_id
JOIN d_items di ON ce.itemid = di.itemid
WHERE icu.subject_id = 10001725
AND icu.stay_id = (
    SELECT MIN(stay_id)
    FROM icustays
    WHERE subject_id = 10001725
)
AND di.label = 'SpO2';
b5ddccb2652019203e02c96e:
WITH SystolicBP AS (
    SELECT 
        ce.charttime,
        ce.valuenum,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY ce.charttime) AS row_num
    FROM 
        chartevents ce
    INNER JOIN 
        d_items di ON ce.itemid = di.itemid
    WHERE 
        ce.subject_id = 10003046 
        AND di.label = 'Systolic Blood Pressure'
),
FirstLastValues AS (
    SELECT 
        MIN(CASE WHEN row_num = 1 THEN valuenum END) AS first_valuenum,
        MIN(CASE WHEN row_num = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SystolicBP) THEN valuenum END) AS last_valuenum
    FROM 
        SystolicBP
)
SELECT 
    (last_valuenum - first_valuenum) AS systolic_bp_change
FROM 
    FirstLastValues;
5ae9eba9c11262b3bc8961b7:
WITH ICUStay AS (
  SELECT 
    icu.stay_id
  FROM 
    icustays icu
  JOIN 
    chartevents ce ON icu.stay_id = ce.stay_id
  WHERE 
    ce.subject_id = 10020187
  LIMIT 1
),
LastTwoMeasurements AS (
  SELECT 
    ce.charttime,
    ce.valuenum
  FROM 
    chartevents ce
  JOIN 
    ICUStay icu ON ce.stay_id = icu.stay_id
  JOIN 
    d_items di ON ce.itemid = di.itemid
  WHERE 
    di.label = 'Systolic Blood Pressure'
  ORDER BY 
    ce.charttime DESC
  LIMIT 2
)
SELECT 
  (SELECT valuenum FROM LastTwoMeasurements LIMIT 1) - 
  (SELECT valuenum FROM LastTwoMeasurements LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1) AS blood_pressure_difference;
617d9b7140ffa467be53e5b8:
WITH FirstReading AS (
    SELECT 
        charttime,
        valuenum
    FROM 
        labevents le
    JOIN 
        d_labitems li ON le.itemid = li.itemid
    WHERE 
        li.label = 'CO2 READING'
        AND le.subject_id = 10039831
    ORDER BY 
        charttime ASC
    LIMIT 1
),
LastReading AS (
    SELECT 
        charttime,
        valuenum
    FROM 
        labevents le
    JOIN 
        d_labitems li ON le.itemid = li.itemid
    WHERE 
        li.label = 'CO2 READING'
        AND le.subject_id = 10039831
    ORDER BY 
        charttime DESC
    LIMIT 1
)
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN fr.valuenum < lr.valuenum THEN 'true'
        ELSE 'false'
    END AS is_smaller
FROM 
    FirstReading fr
CROSS JOIN 
    LastReading lr;
769ea1c5d6c42c47ac9a1735:
WITH LastHadmCTE AS (
    SELECT 
        MAX(hadm_id) AS hadm_id
    FROM 
        admissions
    WHERE 
        subject_id = 10036156
),
FirstLastValuesCTE AS (
    SELECT 
        MIN(charttime) AS first_charttime,
        MAX(charttime) AS last_charttime,
        MIN(valuenum) OVER () AS first_value,
        MAX(valuenum) OVER () AS last_value
    FROM 
        labevents
    INNER JOIN 
        d_labitems ON labevents.itemid = d_labitems.itemid
    INNER JOIN 
        LastHadmCTE ON labevents.hadm_id = LastHadmCTE.hadm_id
    WHERE 
        d_labitems.label = 'PLATELET COUNT'
        AND labevents.subject_id = 10036156
)
SELECT 
    (CASE 
        WHEN last_value > first_value THEN 'Yes'
        ELSE 'No'
    END) AS result
FROM 
    FirstLastValuesCTE;

WITH LastHadm AS (
    SELECT hadm_id
    FROM admissions
    WHERE subject_id = 10016810
    ORDER BY admittime DESC
    LIMIT 1
),
CalciumReadings AS (
    SELECT 
        charttime,
        valuenum AS calcium_value
    FROM labevents
    WHERE subject_id = 10016810
      AND hadm_id = (SELECT hadm_id FROM LastHadm)
      AND itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE label = 'Calcium, Total')
)
SELECT 
    MAX(CASE WHEN charttime = (SELECT MAX(charttime) FROM CalciumReadings) THEN calcium_value END) > 
    MIN(CASE WHEN charttime = (SELECT MIN(charttime) FROM CalciumReadings) THEN calcium_value END) AS is_greater
FROM CalciumReadings;

             FROM chartevents 
             WHERE subject_id = 10020944 
             AND itemid = (SELECT itemid

                              AND stay_id = (SELECT stay_id 
                                             FROM icustays 
                                             WHERE subject_id = 10020944

        THEN 'Yes'

      SELECT stay_id 
      FROM icustays 
      WHERE subject_id = 10019385
    )
    AND charttime < ce_last.charttime
  );

WITH FirstICUVisit AS (
  SELECT 
    stay_id,
    MIN(intime) AS first_intime
  FROM icustays
  WHERE subject_id = 10010471
  GROUP BY stay_id
),
FirstICUStay AS (
  SELECT 
    stay_id
  FROM FirstICUVisit
  ORDER BY first_intime
  LIMIT 1
),
FirstO2Saturation AS (
  SELECT 
    c.valuenum AS first_o2_saturation
  FROM chartevents c
  JOIN FirstICUStay fs ON c.stay_id = fs.stay_id
  WHERE c.itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label = 'O2 saturation pulseoxymetry')
    AND c.charttime = (SELECT MIN(charttime) 
                       FROM chartevents 
                       WHERE stay_id = fs.stay_id 
                         AND itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label = 'O2 saturation pulseoxymetry'))
),
LastO2Saturation AS (
  SELECT 
    c.valuenum AS last_o2_saturation
  FROM chartevents c
  JOIN FirstICUStay fs ON c.stay_id = fs.stay_id
  WHERE c.itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label = 'O2 saturation pulseoxymetry')
    AND c.charttime = (SELECT MAX(charttime) 
                       FROM chartevents 
                       WHERE stay_id = fs.stay_id 
                         AND itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label = 'O2 saturation pulseoxymetry'))
)
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN last_o2_saturation > first_o2_saturation THEN 'YES'
    ELSE 'NO'
  END AS is_last_measurement_greater
FROM FirstO2Saturation, LastO2Saturation;

WITH PatientAge AS (
  SELECT 
    age 
  FROM 
    admissions 
  WHERE 
    subject_id = 10035185 
  ORDER BY 
    admittime 
  LIMIT 1
),
SameAgePatients AS (
  SELECT 
    a.subject_id
  FROM 
    admissions a
  JOIN 
    PatientAge pa ON a.age = pa.age
),
UreaNitrogenValues AS (
  SELECT 
    l.valuenum
  FROM 
    labevents l
  JOIN 
    SameAgePatients sp ON l.subject_id = sp.subject_id
  WHERE 
    l.itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE label = 'Urea Nitrogen')
    AND l.valueuom = 'mg/dL'
)
SELECT 
  PERCENT_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY valuenum) * 100 AS urea_nitrogen_percentile
FROM 
  UreaNitrogenValues
WHERE 
  valuenum = 38.0;

WITH PlateletResults AS (
    SELECT 
        l.subject_id,
        l.charttime,
        l.valuenum,
        a.admittime,
        a.dischtime,
        strftime('%Y', a.admittime) - strftime('%Y', p.dob) AS age_at_time
    FROM 
        labevents l
    INNER JOIN 
        admissions a ON l.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
    INNER JOIN 
        patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
    INNER JOIN 
        d_labitems d ON l.itemid = d.itemid
    WHERE 
        d.label = 'PLATELET COUNT (IU/ML)'
        AND l.subject_id = 10021487
),
PatientAge AS (
    SELECT 
        age_at_time
    FROM 
        PlateletResults
),
AgeGroupPercentile AS (
    SELECT 
        PERCENT_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY age_at_time) AS percentile_rank
    FROM 
        PlateletResults
)
SELECT 
    percentile_rank
FROM 
    AgeGroupPercentile;

SELECT

FROM 
  admissions a
  JOIN labevents l ON a.subject_id = l.subject_id AND a.hadm_id = l.hadm_id
WHERE 
  a.subject_id = 10018081 AND 
  l.itemid IN (
    SELECT itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE label IN ('Electrolyte Panel', 'Serum Na+')
  )
  AND l.valuenum < 300 AND l.valueuom = 'mOsm/kg' -- Hyposmolality
  OR l.valuenum < 135 AND l.valueuom = 'mEq/L'   -- Hyponatremia
ORDER BY 
  l.charttime ASC
LIMIT 1;

WITH TodayPrescriptions AS (
    SELECT drug
    FROM prescriptions
    WHERE subject_id = 10004733
      AND starttime >= DATE('now', 'start of day')
      AND (stoptime IS NULL OR stoptime >= DATE('now', 'start of day'))
),
YesterdayPrescriptions AS (
    SELECT drug
    FROM prescriptions
    WHERE subject_id = 10004733
      AND starttime < DATE('now', 'start of day')
      AND (stoptime IS NULL OR stoptime < DATE('now', 'start of day'))
)
SELECT tp.drug
FROM TodayPrescriptions tp
LEFT JOIN YesterdayPrescriptions yp ON tp.drug = yp.drug
WHERE yp.drug IS NULL;

WITH FirstAdmission AS (
  SELECT
    subject_id,
    hadm_id,
    admittime
  FROM
    admissions
  WHERE
    subject_id = 10004720
  ORDER BY
    admittime
  LIMIT 1
),
NeutrophilLevels AS (
  SELECT
    l.subject_id,
    l.hadm_id,
    l.charttime,
    l.valuenum
  FROM
    labevents l
  INNER JOIN
    FirstAdmission fa ON l.subject_id = fa.subject_id AND l.hadm_id = fa.hadm_id
  INNER JOIN
    d_labitems dl ON l.itemid = dl.itemid
  WHERE
    dl.label LIKE '%Neutrophils%'
)
SELECT
  MIN(charttime) AS first_charttime
FROM
  NeutrophilLevels
WHERE
  valuenum = (
    SELECT
      MAX(valuenum)
    FROM
      NeutrophilLevels
  );

    INNER JOIN PatientICUStay icu ON ce.stay_id = icu.stay_id
    INNER JOIN d_items di ON ce.itemid = di.itemid
    WHERE di.label = 'Blood Pressure'
)
SELECT 
    MIN(charttime) AS first_max_dbp_time
FROM (
    SELECT 
        charttime,
        valuenum,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY valuenum DESC) AS dbp_rank
    FROM DBPEvents
) AS max_dbp_events
WHERE dbp_rank = 1;

WITH PatientICUStay AS (
    SELECT
        icu.stay_id,
        icu.intime,
        icu.outtime,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY icu.intime DESC) AS stay_rank
    FROM icustays icu
    WHERE icu.subject_id = 10019385
),
LastICUStay AS (
    SELECT
        stay_id,
        intime,
        outtime
    FROM PatientICUStay
    WHERE stay_rank = 1
),
SystolicBloodPressure AS (
    SELECT
        lab.charttime,
        lab.valuenum AS systolic_bp
    FROM labevents lab
    INNER JOIN d_labitems dlab ON lab.itemid = dlab.itemid
    INNER JOIN LastICUStay lasticu ON lab.hadm_id = lasticu.stay_id
    WHERE dlab.label = 'Systolic Blood Pressure'
)
SELECT
    DATE(charttime) AS date,
    AVG(systolic_bp) AS avg_systolic_bp
FROM SystolicBloodPressure
GROUP BY DATE(charttime)
ORDER BY date;

WITH MicroscopicHematuriaPatients AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT m.subject_id
  FROM microbiologyevents m
  WHERE m.test_name = 'Microscopic Hematuria'
),
PhytonadionePatients AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT p.subject_id
  FROM prescriptions p
  WHERE p.drug = 'phytonadione'
),
EligiblePatients AS (
  SELECT mh.subject_id
  FROM MicroscopicHematuriaPatients mh
  INNER JOIN PhytonadionePatients ph ON mh.subject_id = ph.subject_id
)
SELECT 
  AVG(CASE WHEN julianday(p.dod) - julianday(p.dob) <= 182.5 THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) AS six_month_survival_rate
FROM patients p
INNER JOIN EligiblePatients ep ON p.subject_id = ep.subject_id
WHERE p.dod IS NOT NULL;

SELECT 
    CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN p.dod IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS survival_rate
FROM 
    patients p
INNER JOIN 
    diagnoses_icd d ON p.subject_id = d.subject_id
INNER JOIN 
    admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
INNER JOIN 
    procedures_icd pr ON a.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
INNER JOIN 
    prescriptions prx ON a.hadm_id = prx.hadm_id
WHERE 
    d.icd_code = 'S06.1'  -- Subdural hemorrhage
    AND pr.icd_code NOT IN ('N98.3')  -- Exclude open intracranial wound
    AND prx.drug = 'Phenobarbital';

WITH PatientSurvival AS (
  SELECT 
    p.subject_id,
    p.dod,
    CASE 
      WHEN p.dod IS NULL THEN 1 
      WHEN p.dod > (julianday(p.dod) - julianday(p.dob)) / 90 THEN 1 
      ELSE 0 
    END AS survived_3_months
  FROM 
    patients p
  INNER JOIN 
    admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
  INNER JOIN 
    diagnoses_icd d ON a.hadm_id = d.hadm_id
  INNER JOIN 
    procedures_icd pr ON a.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
  WHERE 
    d.icd_code = 'F231' AND pr.icd_code = 'N07'
),
TotalPatients AS (
  SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS total_patients
  FROM 
    PatientSurvival
),
SurvivedPatients AS (
  SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS survived_patients
  FROM 
    PatientSurvival
  WHERE 
    survived_3_months = 1
)
SELECT 
  CAST(survived_patients AS REAL) * 100 / total_patients AS survival_rate
FROM 
  TotalPatients, SurvivedPatients;

WITH PneumoniaPatients AS (
    SELECT 
        p.subject_id,
        p.gender,
        p.dob,
        p.dod,
        d.charttime AS diagnosis_time,
        m.charttime AS micro_time,
        pr.starttime AS pr_starttime
    FROM patients p
    INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd d ON p.subject_id = d.subject_id
    INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dcd ON d.icd_code = dcd.icd_code
    INNER JOIN microbiologyevents m ON p.subject_id = m.subject_id AND d.hadm_id = m.hadm_id
    INNER JOIN prescriptions pr ON p.subject_id = pr.subject_id AND d.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
    WHERE dcd.long_title LIKE '%Pneumonia%' 
      AND m.spec_type_desc LIKE '%Klebsiella pneumoniae%' 
      AND pr.drug LIKE '%Insulin%'
      AND pr.starttime > d.charttime
),
SurvivalRates AS (
    SELECT 
        subject_id,
        CASE 
            WHEN (julianday(dod) - julianday(dob)) <= 180 THEN 'Survived'
            ELSE 'Died'
        END AS survival_status
    FROM PneumoniaPatients
)
SELECT 
    AVG(CASE WHEN survival_status = 'Survived' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) * 100 AS survival_rate
FROM SurvivalRates;

WITH poliomyelitis_diagnoses AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT d.subject_id
  FROM diagnoses_icd d
  JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dd ON d.icd_code = dd.icd_code
  WHERE dd.icd_code = 'G80.0'
),
insulin_treatments AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT p.subject_id
  FROM prescriptions p
  WHERE p.drug LIKE '%insulin%'
),
eligible_patients AS (
  SELECT pd.subject_id
  FROM poliomyelitis_diagnoses pd
  JOIN insulin_treatments it ON pd.subject_id = it.subject_id
),
survival_status AS (
  SELECT e.subject_id,
         CASE
           WHEN (julianday(a.dischtime) + 180) > julianday(CURRENT_DATE) THEN 'Alive'
           ELSE 'Deceased'
         END AS survival_status
  FROM eligible_patients e
  JOIN admissions a ON e.subject_id = a.subject_id
)
SELECT COUNT(*) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM eligible_patients) AS survival_rate
FROM survival_status
WHERE survival_status = 'Alive';

WITH 
  MortalityData AS (
    SELECT 
      p.subject_id,
      p.gender,
      p.dob,
      p.dod,
      d_icd.icd_code,
      d_icd.long_title
    FROM 
      patients p
    INNER JOIN 
      diagnoses_icd d ON p.subject_id = d.subject_id
    INNER JOIN 
      d_icd_diagnoses d_icd ON d.icd_code = d_icd.icd_code
    WHERE 
      p.dod IS NOT NULL AND 
      julianday(p.dod) - julianday(p.dob) < 3 * 365
  ),
  DiagnosisCounts AS (
    SELECT 
      long_title,
      COUNT(*) AS mortality_count
    FROM 
      MortalityData
    GROUP BY 
      long_title
    ORDER BY 
      mortality_count DESC
    LIMIT 4
  )
SELECT 
  long_title
FROM 
  DiagnosisCounts;

WITH PatientMortalityCTE AS (
    SELECT p.subject_id,
           CASE 
               WHEN p.dod IS NOT NULL AND DATE(p.dod) <= DATE(a.admittime, '+6 months') THEN 1
               ELSE 0
           END AS six_month_mortality
    FROM patients p
    INNER JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
),
DiagnosisMortalityCTE AS (
    SELECT d.icd_code, d.subject_id, d.hadm_id, pm.six_month_mortality
    FROM diagnoses_icd d
    INNER JOIN PatientMortalityCTE pm ON d.subject_id = pm.subject_id
)
SELECT icd.long_title, COUNT(*) AS mortality_count
FROM DiagnosisMortalityCTE dm
INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses icd ON dm.icd_code = icd.icd_code
WHERE dm.six_month_mortality = 1
GROUP BY icd.long_title
ORDER BY mortality_count DESC
LIMIT 4;
66e468b8ba6fe6d332363ba2:
WITH DiagnosisMortality AS (
    SELECT
        d.long_title AS diagnosis,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.dod <= DATE(a.admittime, '+3 months') THEN 1 END) * 1.0 / COUNT(*) AS mortality_rate
    FROM admissions a
    JOIN diagnoses_icd di ON a.hadm_id = di.hadm_id
    JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON di.icd_code = d.icd_code
    JOIN patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
    GROUP BY d.long_title
),
RankedDiagnoses AS (
    SELECT
        diagnosis,
        mortality_rate,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC) AS mortality_rank
    FROM DiagnosisMortality
)
SELECT diagnosis, mortality_rate
FROM RankedDiagnoses
WHERE mortality_rank <= 3;

SELECT 
    T3.long_title AS Diagnosis, 
    COUNT(T1.subject_id) AS MortalityCount

INNER JOIN

    strftime('%J', T1.dod) - strftime('%J', T1.dob) <= 90

WITH DiagnosisMortalityCTE AS (
  SELECT 
    d_icd_diagnoses.long_title AS diagnosis,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN patients.dod IS NOT NULL AND patients.dod <= DATE(admissions.admittime, '+6 months') THEN 1 END) AS deaths,
    COUNT(*) AS total
  FROM admissions
  JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id
  JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
  JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id
  GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title
),
MortalityRateCTE AS (
  SELECT 
    diagnosis,
    (deaths * 1.0 / total) * 100 AS mortality_rate
  FROM DiagnosisMortalityCTE
)
SELECT 
  diagnosis,
  mortality_rate
FROM MortalityRateCTE
ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC
LIMIT 4;

WITH MonthlyCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        strftime('%Y-%m', a.admittime) AS month,
        COUNT(*) AS monthly_records
    FROM admissions a
    JOIN procedures_icd p ON a.hadm_id = p.hadm_id
    JOIN d_icd_procedures d ON p.icd_code = d.icd_code
    JOIN diagnoses_icd di ON a.hadm_id = di.hadm_id
    JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d_di ON di.icd_code = d_di.icd_code
    WHERE d.long_title LIKE '%Other Reconstructive Surgery%'
      AND (d_di.long_title LIKE '%Abnormal Reaction of the Patient%' 
           OR d_di.long_title LIKE '%Later Complication%')
      AND strftime('%Y', a.admittime) = '2100'
    GROUP BY month
)
SELECT MAX(monthly_records) AS max_monthly_records
FROM MonthlyCounts;

WITH InsulinUsers AS (
  SELECT 
    p.subject_id,
    a.admittime
  FROM 
    patients p
  INNER JOIN 
    admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
  INNER JOIN 
    prescriptions pr ON a.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
  WHERE 
    pr.drug LIKE '%insulin%' 
    AND pr.route LIKE '%subcutaneous%' 
    AND (pr.starttime <= a.admittime AND pr.stoptime >= a.dischtime)
),
MonthlyCounts AS (
  SELECT 
    strftime('%Y-%m', admittime) AS admittime_month,
    COUNT(*) AS patient_count
  FROM 
    InsulinUsers
  GROUP BY 
    admittime_month
)
SELECT 
  MIN(patient_count) AS min_patient_count
FROM 
  MonthlyCounts;

    chartevents c
  WHERE
    c.itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label LIKE '%BMI%')

FROM
  bmi_records
GROUP BY
  month
ORDER BY
  month;

WITH filtered_procedures AS (
    SELECT 
        p.subject_id,
        p.hadm_id,
        pr.icd_code
    FROM 
        admissions p
    INNER JOIN 
        procedures_icd pr ON p.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
    INNER JOIN 
        d_icd_procedures prd ON pr.icd_code = prd.icd_code
    WHERE 
        prd.long_title = 'Resection of vessel with replacement, thoracic vessels'
        AND strftime('%Y-%m', p.admittime) = '2100-01'
),
filtered_diagnoses AS (
    SELECT 
        fp.subject_id,
        fp.hadm_id,
        d.icd_code,
        d.long_title
    FROM 
        filtered_procedures fp
    INNER JOIN 
        diagnoses_icd d ON fp.hadm_id = d.hadm_id
),
diagnosis_counts AS (
    SELECT 
        long_title,
        COUNT(*) as diagnosis_count
    FROM 
        filtered_diagnoses
    GROUP BY 
        long_title
)
SELECT 
    long_title,
    diagnosis_count
FROM 
    diagnosis_counts
ORDER BY 
    diagnosis_count DESC
LIMIT 3;

WITH LaparoscopicProcedures AS (
    SELECT p.subject_id, l.charttime AS procedure_time
    FROM patients p
    INNER JOIN labevents l ON p.subject_id = l.subject_id
    INNER JOIN d_labitems d ON l.itemid = d.itemid
    WHERE l.charttime >= DATE('now', '-1 year')
      AND d.label = 'Laparoscopic lysis of peritoneal adhesions'
),
Diagnoses AS (
    SELECT lp.subject_id, lp.procedure_time, d.long_title AS diagnosis
    FROM LaparoscopicProcedures lp
    INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd di ON lp.subject_id = di.subject_id
    INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON di.icd_code = d.icd_code
    WHERE di.charttime >= lp.procedure_time
      AND di.charttime <= DATE(lp.procedure_time, '+2 months')
)
SELECT diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS frequency
FROM Diagnoses
GROUP BY diagnosis
ORDER BY frequency DESC
LIMIT 3;

WITH SpecificProcedureCTE AS (
  SELECT 
    hadm_id,
    icd_code
  FROM 
    procedures_icd
  WHERE 
    icd_code = (
      SELECT 
        icd_code 
      FROM 
        d_icd_procedures 
      WHERE 
        long_title = 'Extirpation of matter from left lower lobe bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic'
    )
),

DiagnosesAfterProcedureCTE AS (
  SELECT 
    d.subject_id,
    d.hadm_id,
    d.icd_code,
    d.charttime
  FROM 
    diagnoses_icd d
  INNER JOIN 
    SpecificProcedureCTE sp ON d.hadm_id = sp.hadm_id
  WHERE 
    d.charttime BETWEEN (SELECT admittime FROM admissions WHERE hadm_id = sp.hadm_id)
    AND (SELECT admittime FROM admissions WHERE hadm_id = sp.hadm_id) + 60 * 60 * 24 * 60
)

SELECT 
  icd_code,
  COUNT(*) AS diagnosis_count
FROM 
  DiagnosesAfterProcedureCTE
GROUP BY 
  icd_code
ORDER BY 
  diagnosis_count DESC
LIMIT 3;

    INNER JOIN patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
    INNER JOIN EsophagealRefluxDiagnoses er ON a.hadm_id = er.hadm_id
    WHERE age >= 60
),
PrescriptionsWithinTwoMonths AS (
    SELECT 
        p.subject_id,
        p.hadm_id,
        p.starttime,
        p.drug
    FROM prescriptions p
    INNER JOIN FilteredAdmissions fa ON p.subject_id = fa.subject_id AND p.hadm_id = fa.hadm_id
    WHERE p.starttime BETWEEN fa.admittime AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d', fa.dischtime, '+2 months')
)
SELECT 
    drug,
    COUNT(*) AS frequency
FROM PrescriptionsWithinTwoMonths
GROUP BY drug
ORDER BY frequency DESC
LIMIT 4;

GROUP BY dl.label
ORDER BY test_count DESC

50cfc25b33dbf1f04dd32e42:
Select the distinct specimen types (`spec_type_desc`) from the `microbiologyevents` table.
2. Join this table with the `diagnoses_icd` table on `hadm_id` to link the diagnosis to the hospital admission.
3. Filter the diagnoses to those with the code 'E88.00'.
4. Ensure the event time (`charttime`) is within the last year.
5. Group by the specimen type to count occurrences.
6. Order by the count of occurrences in descending order and limit to the top 4.
10c4954997c7b5eab9c3c231:
SELECT 
  T1.test_name,
  COUNT(*) AS frequency
FROM 
  microbiologyevents T1
  INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id
  INNER JOIN admissions T3 ON T2.hadm_id = T3.hadm_id
WHERE 
  T2.icd_code IN (
    SELECT 
      icd_code 
    FROM 
      d_icd_diagnoses 
    WHERE 
      long_title LIKE '%noncompliance with renal dialysis%'
  )
  AND T3.admittime <= T1.charttime 
  AND T1.charttime <= DATE(T3.admittime, '+2 months')
GROUP BY 
  T1.test_name
ORDER BY 
  frequency DESC
LIMIT 5;

MicrobiologyEvents AS (

WITH PatientsWithPackedCellTransfusion AS (
    SELECT
        p.subject_id,
        p.gender,
        p.dob,
        p.dod,
        adm.admittime,
        adm.dischtime,
        adm.admission_type,
        adm.admission_location,
        adm.discharge_location
    FROM patients p

    p.subject_id,

WITH ProcedureCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        p.ipd_code,
        p.long_title,
        COUNT(*) AS procedure_count
    FROM procedures_icd pi
    JOIN d_icd_procedures p ON pi.icd_code = p.icd_code
    GROUP BY p.ipd_code, p.long_title
),
RankedProcedures AS (
    SELECT 
        long_title,
        procedure_count,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY procedure_count DESC) AS rank
    FROM ProcedureCounts
)
SELECT 
    GROUP_CONCAT(long_title, ', ') AS procedure_names,
    GROUP_CONCAT(procedure_count, ', ') AS procedure_counts
FROM RankedProcedures
WHERE rank <= 10;

WITH EngineerPatients AS (
    SELECT subject_id
    FROM patients
    WHERE gender = 'engineer'
),
HypertensionDiagnoses AS (
    SELECT T1.subject_id
    FROM diagnoses_icd T1
    INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses T2 ON T1.icd_code = T2.icd_code
    WHERE T2.long_title LIKE '%hypertension%'
),
EngineerHypertensionPatients AS (
    SELECT T1.subject_id
    FROM EngineerPatients T1
    INNER JOIN HypertensionDiagnoses T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id
)
SELECT 
    (COUNT(*) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM EngineerPatients)) AS HypertensionPercentage
FROM EngineerHypertensionPatients;

c82edfa2a6b5736bd0ba574c:
WITH 
alcohol_admissions AS (
  SELECT 
    a.hadm_id,
    a.admittime,
    a.dischtime,
    (julianday(a.dischtime) - julianday(a.admittime)) AS length_of_stay
  FROM admissions a
  INNER JOIN prescriptions p ON a.hadm_id = p.hadm_id
  WHERE p.drug LIKE '%alcohol%'
),

no_alcohol_admissions AS (
  SELECT 
    a.hadm_id,
    a.admittime,
    a.dischtime,
    (julianday(a.dischtime) - julianday(a.admittime)) AS length_of_stay
  FROM admissions a
  WHERE a.hadm_id NOT IN (SELECT hadm_id FROM alcohol_admissions)
),

average_stays AS (
  SELECT 
    AVG(length_of_stay) AS avg_alcohol_stay
  FROM alcohol_admissions
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    AVG(length_of_stay) AS avg_no_alcohol_stay
  FROM no_alcohol_admissions
)

SELECT 
  a.avg_alcohol_stay,
  b.avg_no_alcohol_stay,
  a.avg_alcohol_stay > b.avg_no_alcohol_stay AS has_longer_stay
FROM average_stays a, average_stays b
WHERE a.avg_alcohol_stay IS NOT NULL AND b.avg_no_alcohol_stay IS NOT NULL;

WITH ICUStayLengths AS (
    SELECT
        c.event_type,
        julianday(icu.outtime) - julianday(icu.intime) AS icu_stay_length
    FROM icustays icu
    INNER JOIN cost c ON icu.hadm_id = c.hadm_id
    WHERE c.event_type IN ('completed', 'delayed')
)
SELECT
    (SELECT SUM(icu_stay_length) FROM ICUStayLengths WHERE event_type = 'completed') -
    (SELECT SUM(icu_stay_length) FROM ICUStayLengths WHERE event_type = 'delayed') AS icu_stay_length_diff;

WITH ExcessivePrescriptions AS (
    SELECT p.subject_id, a.language
    FROM patients p
    JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
    JOIN prescriptions pr ON a.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
    WHERE CAST(pr.dose_val_rx AS REAL) > CAST(pr.dose_unit_rx AS REAL)
)
SELECT language, COUNT(*) as language_count
FROM ExcessivePrescriptions
GROUP BY language
ORDER BY language_count DESC
LIMIT 5;

WITH HypertensionPatients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT a.subject_id
    FROM admissions a
    INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd d ON a.hadm_id = d.hadm_id
    INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dcd ON d.icd_code = dcd.icd_code
    WHERE dcd.long_title LIKE '%Hypertension%'
),
HypertensionMedications AS (
    SELECT p.drug, COUNT(*) AS count
    FROM prescriptions p
    INNER JOIN HypertensionPatients hp ON p.subject_id = hp.subject_id
    GROUP BY p.drug
)
SELECT drug AS recommended_drug
FROM HypertensionMedications
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 1;

FROM 
  icustays i
  INNER JOIN admissions a ON i.hadm_id = a.hadm_id

WITH FirstChildAgeCTE AS (
    SELECT p.subject_id, 
           (julianday(a.admittime) - julianday(p.dob)) / 365.25 AS age
    FROM patients p
    INNER JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
    WHERE a.admittime >= date('now', '-1 month')
    AND p.gender = 'F'  -- Assuming we are calculating for female patients
    AND p.dob IS NOT NULL
    AND p.dod IS NULL
    AND p.row_id = (
        SELECT MIN(p2.row_id)
        FROM patients p2
        WHERE p2.gender = 'F'
        AND p2.dob > p.dob
        AND p2.dod IS NULL
    )
),
RankedChildrenCTE AS (
    SELECT age, 
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY age) AS row_num,
           COUNT(*) OVER () AS total_count
    FROM FirstChildAgeCTE
)
SELECT AVG(age) AS median_age
FROM RankedChildrenCTE
WHERE row_num IN ((total_count + 1) / 2, (total_count + 2) / 2);

WITH procedure_durations AS (
  SELECT 
    p.icd_code,
    AVG(julianday(p.charttime) - julianday(a.starttime)) AS avg_duration
  FROM 
    procedures_icd p
  JOIN 
    inputevents a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id AND p.hadm_id = a.hadm_id AND p.charttime = a.starttime
  WHERE 
    a.totalamountuom = 'uL' AND a.itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label LIKE '%Anesthetic%')
  GROUP BY 
    p.icd_code
)

  FROM admissions a
